#: ../../../doc/en/announce/sprint2016.rst:58
msgid ""
"Other contributors and experienced newcomers are invited to join as well but "
"please send a mail to the pytest-dev mailing list if you intend to do so "
"somewhat soon, also how much funding you need if so.  And if you are working "
"for a company and using pytest heavily you are welcome to join and we "
"encourage your company to provide some funding for the sprint.  They may see "
"it, and rightfully so, as a very cheap and deep training which brings you "
"together with the experts in the field :)"
msgstr ""

